<li class="Studio" value="1">Klik op een oppervlakte- of volumemeting om het te selecteren.</li>
<li class="Studio" value="2">
<p class="list">In de<b>Uiterlijk</b>afdeling van de<a href="../Menus/Window/Panels/Properties/Properties--MV.htm">Eigenschappenpaneel</a>, klik<b>Centroid tonen</b>.</p>
<p>
<img src="https://support.bluebeam.com/online-help/revu21/Content/Resources/Images/Examples/centroid-example.png"/>
</p>
<p>Alternatief, klik<img src="https://support.bluebeam.com/online-help/revu21/Content/Resources/Images/Markup/show_centroid_light.png"/>
<strong class="object">Centroid tonen</strong>in de<strong>Meeteigenschappen</strong>afdeling van de<a data-mc-conditions="Default.Unbind-TrainingManual" data-mc-exclude-action="unbind" href="../Menus/Window/Panels/Measurements/Measure-Tab--MV.htm">Meetpaneel</a>.</p>
